&lt;p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">&lt;span style=" font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:8.25pt;">Part from https://www.nutsvolts.com/magazine/article/november2012_SmileysWorkshop. Breadboard and icon images modified to be 0.3&amp;quot; in spacing and be more similar to the actual physical part.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&lt;/body>&lt;/html></description>
